[
    {
        "text": "When you're 28, science discovers a drug that stops all effects of aging, creating immortality.",
        "source": "api",
        "start_time": 0.0,
        "end_time": 0.0,
        "start_progress": 0.0,
        "end_progress": 0.045366795366795366
    },
    {
        "text": "Your government decides to give the drug to all citizens under 26, but you and the rest of the \"Lost Generations\" are deemed too high-risk.",
        "source": "api",
        "start_time": 0.0,
        "end_time": 0.0,
        "start_progress": 0.04584942084942085,
        "end_progress": 0.11293436293436293
    },
    {
        "text": "When you're 85, the side effects are finally discovered.",
        "source": "api",
        "start_time": 0.0,
        "end_time": 0.0,
        "start_progress": 0.11341698841698841,
        "end_progress": 0.14044401544401544
    },
    {
        "text": "It turns out you could have taken the drug.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 0.0,
        "end_time": 32.0,
        "start_progress": 0.14092664092664092,
        "end_progress": 0.16216216216216217
    },
    {
        "text": "You could have avoided aging, for all of these past years.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 32.0,
        "end_time": 43.0,
        "start_progress": 0.16264478764478765,
        "end_progress": 0.19063706563706564
    },
    {
        "text": "You could have been immortal.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 43.0,
        "end_time": 57.0,
        "start_progress": 0.19111969111969113,
        "end_progress": 0.20511583011583012
    },
    {
        "text": "At 85, you are tired.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 57.0,
        "end_time": 85.0,
        "start_progress": 0.2055984555984556,
        "end_progress": 0.21573359073359075
    },
    {
        "text": "You no longer have the energy to consider all of the options of a younger person.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 85.0,
        "end_time": 100.0,
        "start_progress": 0.21621621621621623,
        "end_progress": 0.2553088803088803
    },
    {
        "text": "All of the things that you could have done seem so far in the past.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 100.0,
        "end_time": 116.0,
        "start_progress": 0.2557915057915058,
        "end_progress": 0.28812741312741313
    },
    {
        "text": "You don't want to stop the aging process now.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 116.0,
        "end_time": 134.0,
        "start_progress": 0.2886100386100386,
        "end_progress": 0.31032818532818535
    },
    {
        "text": "It's too late to live forever.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 134.0,
        "end_time": 138.0,
        "start_progress": 0.3108108108108108,
        "end_progress": 0.3252895752895753
    },
    {
        "text": "What do you do?",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 138.0,
        "end_time": 172.0,
        "start_progress": 0.32577220077220076,
        "end_progress": 0.333976833976834
    },
    {
        "text": "You could take the drug now and still watch your grandchildren grow up.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 172.0,
        "end_time": 196.0,
        "start_progress": 0.3344594594594595,
        "end_progress": 0.3687258687258687
    },
    {
        "text": "You could watch their grandchildren grow up, for that matter.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 196.0,
        "end_time": 206.0,
        "start_progress": 0.3692084942084942,
        "end_progress": 0.39864864864864863
    },
    {
        "text": "Barring any accidents or new diseases, that science hasn't learned how to treat effectively, you could basically live forever.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 206.0,
        "end_time": 235.0,
        "start_progress": 0.39913127413127414,
        "end_progress": 0.45994208494208494
    },
    {
        "text": "But, you've already seen your grandchildren grow up.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 235.0,
        "end_time": 252.0,
        "start_progress": 0.46042471042471045,
        "end_progress": 0.4855212355212355
    },
    {
        "text": "They are already taking the anti-aging drug.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 252.0,
        "end_time": 262.0,
        "start_progress": 0.486003861003861,
        "end_progress": 0.5072393822393823
    },
    {
        "text": "You just can't know if it's worth doing it all, over again, from the point of view of a tired, 85 year old man.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 262.0,
        "end_time": 285.0,
        "start_progress": 0.5077220077220077,
        "end_progress": 0.5612934362934363
    },
    {
        "text": "This is the central question of the story.",
        "source": "api",
        "start_time": 285.0,
        "end_time": 301.0,
        "start_progress": 0.5617760617760618,
        "end_progress": 0.5825289575289575
    },
    {
        "text": "How much life is too much living?",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 301.0,
        "end_time": 317.0,
        "start_progress": 0.583011583011583,
        "end_progress": 0.5989382239382239
    },
    {
        "text": "How much is enough?",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 317.0,
        "end_time": 330.0,
        "start_progress": 0.5994208494208494,
        "end_progress": 0.6085907335907336
    },
    {
        "text": "You can ponder this question until the end of time, taking the drug to buy more days of contemplation.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 330.0,
        "end_time": 360.0,
        "start_progress": 0.609073359073359,
        "end_progress": 0.6583011583011583
    },
    {
        "text": "Or, you can simply die.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 360.0,
        "end_time": 366.0,
        "start_progress": 0.6587837837837838,
        "end_progress": 0.6698841698841699
    },
    {
        "text": "You can die, knowing that you've lived a full life.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 366.0,
        "end_time": 397.0,
        "start_progress": 0.6703667953667953,
        "end_progress": 0.694980694980695
    },
    {
        "text": "Only one life, but that was the deal.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 397.0,
        "end_time": 416.0,
        "start_progress": 0.6954633204633205,
        "end_progress": 0.7133204633204633
    },
    {
        "text": "You took the deal.",
        "source": "api",
        "start_time": 416.0,
        "end_time": 431.0,
        "start_progress": 0.7138030888030888,
        "end_progress": 0.7224903474903475
    },
    {
        "text": "You don't want to extend your life, only out of fear.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 431.0,
        "end_time": 456.0,
        "start_progress": 0.722972972972973,
        "end_progress": 0.749034749034749
    },
    {
        "text": "You don't want to end it out of fear either.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 456.0,
        "end_time": 464.0,
        "start_progress": 0.7495173745173745,
        "end_progress": 0.7707528957528957
    },
    {
        "text": "You want this decision to be based on what has happened and what could still happen, from a hopeful perspective.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 464.0,
        "end_time": 493.0,
        "start_progress": 0.7712355212355212,
        "end_progress": 0.8252895752895753
    },
    {
        "text": "You just can't know if it's realistic to look forward to a bright future.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 493.0,
        "end_time": 514.0,
        "start_progress": 0.8257722007722008,
        "end_progress": 0.861003861003861
    },
    {
        "text": "It's all a gamble, and you just don't know if you want to ante up again.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 514.0,
        "end_time": 532.0,
        "start_progress": 0.8614864864864865,
        "end_progress": 0.8962355212355212
    },
    {
        "text": "It's a very difficult decision.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 532.0,
        "end_time": 543.0,
        "start_progress": 0.8967181467181468,
        "end_progress": 0.9116795366795367
    },
    {
        "text": "The story is told from the perspective of a man named John, who is 85.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 543.0,
        "end_time": 571.0,
        "start_progress": 0.9121621621621622,
        "end_progress": 0.946911196911197
    },
    {
        "text": "In the end, he decided to let go and allow himself to die.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 571.0,
        "end_time": 598.0,
        "start_progress": 0.9473938223938224,
        "end_progress": 0.9753861003861004
    },
    {
        "text": "We will never know if that was the right choice.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 598.0,
        "end_time": 611.0,
        "start_progress": 0.9758687258687259,
        "end_progress": 0.999034749034749
    }
]